{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/Spring/220720-message-converter/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Woody","author":"Woody","siteUrl":"https://gintooooonic.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"gintooooonic/gintooooonic.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"26ddece6-01ed-5fc4-9dc2-b028cc5cc057","excerpt":"HTTP 메시지 컨버터 HTTP API처럼 JSON 데이터를 HTTP 바디에서 읽고 쓰는 경우, HTTP 메시지 컨버터를 사용하는 것이 편리 HTTP 요청의 경우, 와 ()일때 메시지 컨버터가 사용됨 HTTP 응답의 경우, 와 ()일때 메시지 컨버터가 사용됨 HttpMessageConverter 인터페이스와 구현체 Spring Boot에서 사용하는 기본 메시지 컨버터는 다음과 같다. ByteArrayHttpMessageConverter : byte…","html":"<h2 id=\"http-메시지-컨버터\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#http-%EB%A9%94%EC%8B%9C%EC%A7%80-%EC%BB%A8%EB%B2%84%ED%84%B0\" aria-label=\"http 메시지 컨버터 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HTTP 메시지 컨버터</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>HTTP API처럼 JSON 데이터를 HTTP 바디에서 읽고 쓰는 경우, HTTP 메시지 컨버터를 사용하는 것이 편리</li>\n<li>HTTP 요청의 경우, <code class=\"language-text\">@RequestBody</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">HttpEntity</code>(<code class=\"language-text\">RequestEntity</code>)일때 메시지 컨버터가 사용됨</li>\n<li>HTTP 응답의 경우, <code class=\"language-text\">@ResponseBody</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">HttpEntity</code>(<code class=\"language-text\">ResponseEntity</code>)일때 메시지 컨버터가 사용됨</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"httpmessageconverter-인터페이스와-구현체\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#httpmessageconverter-%EC%9D%B8%ED%84%B0%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%8A%A4%EC%99%80-%EA%B5%AC%ED%98%84%EC%B2%B4\" aria-label=\"httpmessageconverter 인터페이스와 구현체 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HttpMessageConverter 인터페이스와 구현체</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">package</span> <span class=\"token namespace\">org<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>springframework<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>http<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>converter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">interface</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">HttpMessageConverter</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">T</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">boolean</span> <span class=\"token function\">canRead</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Class</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">?</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> clazz<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Nullable</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MediaType</span> mediaType<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">boolean</span> <span class=\"token function\">canWrite</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Class</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">?</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> clazz<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Nullable</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MediaType</span> mediaType<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token class-name\">List</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">MediaType</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> <span class=\"token function\">getSupportedMediaTypes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token class-name\">T</span> <span class=\"token function\">read</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Class</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">T</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> clazz<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">HttpInputMessage</span> inputMessage<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">throws</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">IOException</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">HttpMessageNotReadableException</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">write</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">T</span> t<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Nullable</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MediaType</span> contentType<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">HttpOutputMessage</span> outputMessage<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">throws</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">IOException</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">HttpMessageNotWritableException</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Spring Boot에서 사용하는 기본 메시지 컨버터는 다음과 같다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ByteArrayHttpMessageConverter : byte[] 데이터를 처리한다.</li>\n<li>StringHttpMessageConverter : String 문자로 데이터를 처리한다.</li>\n<li>MappingJackson2HttpMessageConverter : application/json</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"http-요청과-응답에서의-동작-흐름\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#http-%EC%9A%94%EC%B2%AD%EA%B3%BC-%EC%9D%91%EB%8B%B5%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C%EC%9D%98-%EB%8F%99%EC%9E%91-%ED%9D%90%EB%A6%84\" aria-label=\"http 요청과 응답에서의 동작 흐름 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HTTP 요청과 응답에서의 동작 흐름</h2>\n<h3 id=\"http-요청\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#http-%EC%9A%94%EC%B2%AD\" aria-label=\"http 요청 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HTTP 요청</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>HTTP 요청이 오고, 컨트롤러에서 <code class=\"language-text\">@RequestBody</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">HttpEntity</code> 파라미터를 사용한다.</li>\n<li>\n<p>메시지 컨버터가 메시지를 읽을 수 있는지 확인하기 위해 <code class=\"language-text\">canRead()</code>를 호출한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>대상 클래스 타입을 지원하는지</li>\n<li>해당 Content-Type 미디어 타입을 지원하는지</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">canRead()</code> 조건을 만족하는 경우 <code class=\"language-text\">read()</code>를 호출해 객체를 생성하고 반환한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"http-응답\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#http-%EC%9D%91%EB%8B%B5\" aria-label=\"http 응답 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HTTP 응답</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>컨트롤러에서 <code class=\"language-text\">@ResponseBody</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">HttpEntity</code>로 값이 반환된다.</li>\n<li>\n<p>메시지 컨버터가 메시지륻 쓸 수 있는지 확인하기 위해 <code class=\"language-text\">canWrite()</code>를 호출한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>대상 클래스 타입을 지원하는지</li>\n<li>해당 Content-Type 미디어 타입을 지원하는지</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">canWrite()</code> 조건을 만족하면 <code class=\"language-text\">write()</code>를 호출해 HTTP 응답 메시지 바디에 데이터를 생성한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"argumentresolver와-returnvaluehandler\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#argumentresolver%EC%99%80-returnvaluehandler\" aria-label=\"argumentresolver와 returnvaluehandler permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ArgumentResolver와 ReturnValueHandler</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"message-converter\"\n        title=\"message-converter\"\n        src=\"/static/c17fd9b8eab38974465bd32b58b0e3b8/c1b63/message-converter.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c17fd9b8eab38974465bd32b58b0e3b8/5a46d/message-converter.png 300w,\n/static/c17fd9b8eab38974465bd32b58b0e3b8/0a47e/message-converter.png 600w,\n/static/c17fd9b8eab38974465bd32b58b0e3b8/c1b63/message-converter.png 1200w,\n/static/c17fd9b8eab38974465bd32b58b0e3b8/acf8f/message-converter.png 1340w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"argumentresolver\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#argumentresolver\" aria-label=\"argumentresolver permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ArgumentResolver</h3>\n<p>핸들러를 작성하다보면 메서드의 파라미터를 굉장히 다양하게 구성할 수 있다.\n필요한 값이 있으면 파라미터로 추가해 받아올 수 있도록 유연성을 제공한다.</p>\n<p>이런 부분을 ArgumentResolver가 담당한다.\n<code class=\"language-text\">@RequestMapping</code>의 핸들러 어댑터인 <code class=\"language-text\">RequestMappingHandlerAdapter</code>가\n<code class=\"language-text\">ArgumentResolver</code>를 호출해 핸들러가 필요로 하는 다양한 파라미터의 객체를 생성한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">interface</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">HandlerMethodArgumentResolver</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">boolean</span> <span class=\"token function\">supportsParameter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">MethodParameter</span> parameter<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Nullable</span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">Object</span> <span class=\"token function\">resolveArgument</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">MethodParameter</span> parameter<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Nullable</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ModelAndViewContainer</span> mavContainer<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">NativeWebRequest</span> webRequest<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Nullable</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">WebDataBinderFactory</span> binderFactory<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">throws</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Exception</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>ArgumentResolver는 <code class=\"language-text\">supprtsParameter()</code>를 호출해 해당 파라미터를 지원하는지 확인하고,\n<code class=\"language-text\">resolveArgument()</code>를 호출해 실제 객체를 생성한다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"returnvaluehandler\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#returnvaluehandler\" aria-label=\"returnvaluehandler permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ReturnValueHandler</h3>\n<p>ReturnValueHandler는 핸들러의 반환 타입에 유연성을 제공한다.\n컨트롤러에서 뷰 이름을 반환해도 뷰를 띄울 수 있는 이유가 ReturnValueHandler 때문이다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.inflearn.com/course/%EC%8A%A4%ED%94%84%EB%A7%81-mvc-1\">김영한, 스프링 MVC 1편 - 백엔드 웹 개발 핵심 기술</a></li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Spring/220720-message-converter/#http-%EB%A9%94%EC%8B%9C%EC%A7%80-%EC%BB%A8%EB%B2%84%ED%84%B0\">HTTP 메시지 컨버터</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Spring/220720-message-converter/#httpmessageconverter-%EC%9D%B8%ED%84%B0%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%8A%A4%EC%99%80-%EA%B5%AC%ED%98%84%EC%B2%B4\">HttpMessageConverter 인터페이스와 구현체</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/Spring/220720-message-converter/#http-%EC%9A%94%EC%B2%AD%EA%B3%BC-%EC%9D%91%EB%8B%B5%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C%EC%9D%98-%EB%8F%99%EC%9E%91-%ED%9D%90%EB%A6%84\">HTTP 요청과 응답에서의 동작 흐름</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Spring/220720-message-converter/#http-%EC%9A%94%EC%B2%AD\">HTTP 요청</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Spring/220720-message-converter/#http-%EC%9D%91%EB%8B%B5\">HTTP 응답</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/Spring/220720-message-converter/#argumentresolver%EC%99%80-returnvaluehandler\">ArgumentResolver와 ReturnValueHandler</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Spring/220720-message-converter/#argumentresolver\">ArgumentResolver</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Spring/220720-message-converter/#returnvaluehandler\">ReturnValueHandler</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Spring/220720-message-converter/#reference\">Reference</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"HTTP 메시지 컨버터","date":"July 20, 2022"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Spring/220720-message-converter/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Spring/220720-response/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"HTTP API에서 응답하기"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2486386679","3128451518"]}